[SN]TITLE[SN]
Worcester Warriors: Jan McGinity appointed head of rugby recruitment

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Premiership side Worcester Warriors have appointed Jan McGinity as their new head of rugby recruitment.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
McGinity has previously worked as a consultant at the club and was head of rugby at a sport marketing company.
Worcester finished 10th in the Premiership table last season, 15 points clear of relegation.
"It has become apparent that a club's long-term recruitment strategy is crucial to building its success," chief executive Jim O'Toole said.
